    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="IDEA-gradle突然报错系统找不到指定的路径-Could-not-read-workspace-metadata-from"><a href="#IDEA-gradle突然报错系统找不到指定的路径-Could-not-read-workspace-metadata-from" class="headerlink" title="IDEA gradle突然报错系统找不到指定的路径  Could not read workspace metadata from"></a>IDEA gradle突然报错系统找不到指定的路径  Could not read workspace metadata from</h2><pre><code class="hljs">直接gradle设置里指定新的gradle user home文件夹，刷新gradle后解决</code></pre><h2 id="postman调试接口404-NOT-FOUND"><a href="#postman调试接口404-NOT-FOUND" class="headerlink" title="postman调试接口404 NOT FOUND"></a>postman调试接口404 NOT FOUND</h2><pre><code class="hljs">[流汗]新模块的gralde依赖没有加到总的app里，一定要加上啊！！！</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
    
